Package: simpleclustsim
Title: Simulation Studies for Adaptively-Structured Mixed Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Helen", "Ogden", , "heogden12@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7204-9776"))
Description: Contains code and processed simulation summaries used for the
    simulation studies in the paper "Adaptively-Structured Mixed Models for
    Simple Clustered Data". The repository is intended as a research-code
    archive accompanying the paper, rather than as a general-purpose simulation
    package.
